who'll show interest.

546
00:56:31,978 --> 00:56:36,149
Don't use those.
Use the frosted glasses.

547
00:56:36,358 --> 00:56:40,529
- I warmed up some chicken.
- I love you.

548
00:56:40,737 --> 00:56:44,492
I won't say any more,
but what about Ray?

549
00:56:44,700 --> 00:56:49,288
He shouldn't hear
a strange man's voice in the house.

550
00:56:49,497 --> 00:56:54,920
- A drunken man's voice.
- What about ten angry women?

551
00:56:55,024 --> 00:56:58,361
Lean forward. Okay, I've got it.

552
00:56:58,569 --> 00:57:01,801
