to the zoo and I loved it.

581
00:59:37,384 --> 00:59:44,683
- Let me tell you about my dad.
- No, let's go to the zoo.

582
00:59:44,892 --> 00:59:48,854
Okay, you're right.

583
00:59:48,959 --> 00:59:55,319
My whole life I've been
trying to talk... really talk.

584
00:59:55,529 --> 00:59:59,699
But no one wants to listen.
You know that feeling?

585
00:59:59,908 --> 01:00:04,183
- They just look at you...
- Let's go to the zoo, right now.

586
01:00:04,392 --> 01:00:10,752
The zoo...
the fucking zoo's closed, Ray.

587
01:00:11,796 --> 01:00:17,531
- You said "fuck".
- Yeah, I did.

588
01:00:17,635 --> 01:00:22,224
- Is that...?
- I won't tell.

589
01:00:22,432 --> 01:00:29,001
Well... then I'm gonna have to
take you to the zoo.

590
01:00:29,210 --> 01:00:34,007
