Good catch.

626
01:05:08,465 --> 01:05:13,471
- He needs a contract, Dennis.
- I'll be at The Crocodile at eight.

627
01:05:14,722 --> 01:05:16,808
You bet.

628
01:05:37,246 --> 01:05:41,313
What happened last night?
