629
01:05:41,417 --> 01:05:45,796
- Something came up.
- Okay. $10 million for four years.

630
01:05:46,006 --> 01:05:49,134
- You're dreaming.
- Ten for four.

631
01:05:49,343 --> 01:05:55,390
- He's got an attitude problem.
- He listens to me.

632
01:05:55,599 --> 01:06:00,187
- He's a shrimp.
- He broke all records last year.

633
01:06:00,292 --> 01:06:04,358
I want a prototypical wide-receiver.
6'3", 220 lbs.

634
01:06:04,567 --> 01:06:07,904
Not some shrimp who bitches.

635
01:06:08,113 --> 01:06:14,265
Dennis, I'm asking you...
for a favour.

636
01:06:14,369 --> 01:06:20,104
I introduced you to your wife.
We've spent Christmas together.

637
01:06:20,208 --> 01:06:24,171
- Holiday cheer.
- Jerry, you're reaching.

638
01:06:24,380 --> 01:06:29,177
I'm asking you for a favour.
We have history, Dennis.

639
