649
01:07:31,638 --> 01:07:39,355
- Great word... towel?
- No, I air-dry.

650
01:07:39,459 --> 01:07:44,986
Listen, Rod... I say this
with great respect for you.

651
01:07:46,238 --> 01:07:51,452
