fully tell you about, okay?

667
01:09:12,892 --> 01:09:16,334
God, help me.

668
01:09:16,438 --> 01:09:23,424
Help me.
Help me... help you.

669
01:09:23,633 --> 01:09:27,074
Help me help you.

670
01:09:33,852 --> 01:09:36,667
I'm sorry.

671
01:09:36,772 --> 01:09:41,569
You are hanging on
