674
01:09:50,329 --> 01:09:54,916
- That's my man.
- Hey, I'm happy to entertain you.

675
01:09:55,125 --> 01:10:00,130
- Help me!
- See you in Los Angeles.

676
01:10:00,338 --> 01:10:03,676
Jerry... come on, man.

677
01:10:03,885 --> 01:10:10,558
