we're finally talking.

678
01:10:15,251 --> 01:10:19,421
Unless you love everybody,
you can't sell anybody.

679
01:10:29,119 --> 01:10:34,229
Dennis Wilburn is faxing his offer
for Tidwell on Thursday morning.

680
01:10:34,437 --> 01:10:38,296
- He said you'd be happy... glad.
- Happy or glad?

681
01:10:39,756 --> 01:10:42,675
Glad. He said glad.

682
01:10:43,510 --> 01:10:48,933
- Glad is good.
- We could sure use that commission.

683
01:10:49,141 --> 01:10:53,833
